{"tid":2133161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦即日發稿撐DQ 「愛國者為主體治港」","createTime":"2020-07-31T01:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:19:53.000Z","uid":363119,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c57eb251db8f614442c915726cc45488f0e22c62","tid":2133161,"uid":363119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】政府昨日公布選舉主任DQ民主派參選人，中聯辦即日發聲明，稱堅決支持選舉主任的決定，有關決定理據充足、合法合規。發言人稱，被DQ參選人的言行均突破法律底線，包括公開鼓吹港獨、自決；「告洋狀」求外部勢力制裁香港；宣稱當選後無差別否決財政預算案和政府法案；從根本反對國安法等。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，已故中共領導人鄧小平早指出「港人治港」具界線和標準，就是必須由愛國者為主體的港人治理香港，稱真誠擁護基本法、效忠特區是香港從政者的基本政治要求，亦是從政者理應遵從的政治倫理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200731/s00001/1596134541406/中聯辦即日發稿撐dq-愛國者為主體治港 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200731%2Fs00001%2F1596134541406%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%A8%BF%E6%92%90dq-%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E9%AB%94%E6%B2%BB%E6%B8%AF%20&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1wPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=4846f56d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200731%2Fs00001%2F1596134541406%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%A8%BF%E6%92%90dq-%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%80%85%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB%E9%AB%94%E6%B2%BB%E6%B8%AF%20&h=ae9ab026\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20200731/s00001/1596134541406/中聯辦即日發稿撐dq-愛國者為主體治港 </a>"},{"pid":"7b038cb8d9a21be3a2f675ba4ca823bcc4e1f74d","tid":2133161,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"共人治港"},{"pid":"0c9136852441a87942e8ca0c0931ae0da7eb88e3","tid":2133161,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"共匪吞併香港"},{"pid":"a8abea4d26134568e78bb512161f7f5db4f4d66d","tid":2133161,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31